Paper: hep-th/9210080

Date: 1992-10-14

Title: On The Hamiltonian Structures and The Reductions of The KP Hierarchy

Authors: Didier A Depireux and Jeremy Schiff

Comments: 8 pages with harvmac, IASSNS-HEP-92/66, LAVAL PHY-26-92

Recent work on a free field realization of the Hamiltonian structures of theclassical KP hierarchy and of its flows is reviewed. It is shown that itcorresponds to a reduction of KP to the NLS system. (Talk given by D.A.D. atthe NSERC-CAP Workshop on Quantum Groups, Integrable Models and StatisticalSystems, Kingston, Canada July 13-17 1992.)